<text top="1188" left="70" width="830" height="56" font="font7" id="p1_t29" reading_order_no="29" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">Project  management  has  overall  management </text>
<text top="1237" left="70" width="829" height="55" font="font8" id="p1_t30" reading_order_no="30" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">responsibility  for  the  project  and  the  authority  to </text>
<text top="1284" left="69" width="830" height="56" font="font7" id="p1_t31" reading_order_no="31" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">commit  resources.  SwSE  determines  the  technical </text>
<text top="1333" left="70" width="829" height="55" font="font8" id="p1_t32" reading_order_no="32" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">approach,  makes  technical  decisions,  interfaces </text>
<text top="1381" left="70" width="830" height="55" font="font8" id="p1_t33" reading_order_no="33" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">with  the  technical  acquirer,  and  approves  and </text>
<text top="1428" left="70" width="829" height="56" font="font7" id="p1_t34" reading_order_no="34" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">accepts  the  final  software  product.  SwE  is  respon- </text>
<text top="1476" left="71" width="829" height="56" font="font7" id="p1_t35" reading_order_no="35" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">sible  for  developing  the  software  design,  coding  the </text>
<text top="1524" left="71" width="758" height="56" font="font7" id="p1_t36" reading_order_no="36" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">design,  and  developing  software  components. </text>
<text top="1614" left="70" width="543" height="62" font="font0" id="p1_t37" reading_order_no="37" segment_no="8" tag_type="title">THE  FUNCTIONS  OF  SOFTWARE </text>
